arStrings.szText:
Every {c_number}[SF_0]th{/c} time you deal direct damage to an enemy with a {c_important}Jaguar{/c} Skill, unleash an additional strike dealing {c_number}[SF_1 * 100|%|]{/c} of the damage you have dealt to them in the last {c_number}[SF_3 * SF_4|1|]{/c} seconds.

All Skills are now also {c_important}Jaguar{/c} Skills.
